{
  "name": "02 — Scene Generation Orchestrator (Replicate → HF Router)",
  "nodes": [
    {
      "parameters": {
        "httpMethod": "POST",
        "path": "scene-generation",
        "responseMode": "onReceived",
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "webhook-trigger",
      "name": "Webhook Trigger",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.webhook",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [240, 520],
      "webhookId": "scene-generation-webhook",
      "notes": "Recebe pedido do Python: scene_id, job_id, prompt, callback_url, metadata."
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## Orquestrador (YouTube Dark)\n\nAlinhado ao `video_generator.py`:\n\n1. **Replicate Wan 2.6** (720p, 5s — ~$0,25/clip)\n2. **HF Router → fal.ai Wan2.2** (~US$ 0,10/mês HF)\n\nKling Web (grátis) e fal.ai Kling 2.6 Pro rodam no Python antes do n8n.\n\nCredenciais:\n- `Replicate API Token` → Authorization: Token …\n- `Hugging Face API Token` → Authorization: Bearer …\n- `Pipeline API Key` → X-API-Key",
        "height": 280,
        "width": 460
      },
      "id": "sticky-note-main",
      "name": "Nota — Orquestrador Free",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [120, 120]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "mode": "manual",
        "duplicateItem": false,
        "assignments": {
          "assignments": [
            {
              "id": "scene_id",
              "name": "scene_id",
              "value": "={{ $json.body.scene_id }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "job_id",
              "name": "job_id",
              "value": "={{ $json.body.job_id }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "prompt",
              "name": "prompt",
              "value": "={{ $json.body.prompt }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "callback_url",
              "name": "callback_url",
              "value": "={{ $json.body.callback_url }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "metadata",
              "name": "metadata",
              "value": "={{ $json.body.metadata || {} }}",
              "type": "object"
            },
            {
              "id": "aspect_ratio",
              "name": "aspect_ratio",
              "value": "={{ $json.body.metadata?.aspect_ratio || '16:9' }}",
              "type": "string"
            },
            {
              "id": "negative_prompt",
              "name": "negative_prompt",
              "value": "={{ $json.body.metadata?.negative_prompt || 'blurry, distorted, low quality, watermark, overexposed, shaky camera, text overlay, cartoon' }}",
              "type": "string"
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "set-normalize",
      "name": "Set — Normalizar Payload",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.set",
      "typeVersion": 3.4,
      "position": [480, 520]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "POST",
        "url": "https://api.replicate.com/v1/models/wan-video/wan-2.6-t2v/predictions",
        "authentication": "genericCredentialType",
        "genericAuthType": "httpHeaderAuth",
        "sendBody": true,
        "specifyBody": "json",
        "jsonBody": "={\n  \"input\": {\n    \"prompt\": {{ JSON.stringify($('Set — Normalizar Payload').item.json.prompt) }},\n    \"negative_prompt\": {{ JSON.stringify($('Set — Normalizar Payload').item.json.negative_prompt) }},\n    \"aspect_ratio\": {{ JSON.stringify($('Set — Normalizar Payload').item.json.aspect_ratio) }},\n    \"resolution\": \"720p\",\n    \"duration\": 5,\n    \"enable_prompt_expansion\": true\n  }\n}",
        "options": {
          "timeout": 120000,
          "response": {
            "response": {
              "neverError": true
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "id": "http-replicate-create",
      "name": "HTTP — Replicate Create",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [720, 520],
      "onError": "continueRegularOutput",
      "credentials": {
        "httpHeaderAuth": {
          "id": "REPLICATE_CREDENTIAL_ID",
          "name": "Replicate API Token"
        }
      },
      "notes": "Inicia prediction Wan 2.6 T2V (wan-video/wan-2.6-t2v, 720p 5s)."
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": {
            "caseSensitive": true,
            "leftValue": "",
            "typeValidation": "loose"
          },
          "conditions": [
            {
              "id": "rep-has-id",
              "leftValue": "={{ $json.id || '' }}",
              "rightValue": "",
              "operator": {
                "type": "string",
                "operation": "notEmpty"
              }
            }
          ],
          "combinator": "and"
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "if-replicate-created",
      "name": "IF Replicate Created?",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [900, 520],
      "notes": "Se Create falhar (401/402), cai direto no HF Router."
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "amount": 20,
        "unit": "seconds"
      },
      "id": "wait-replicate-initial",
      "name": "Wait — Replicate 20s",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.wait",
      "typeVersion": 1.1,
      "position": [960, 520],
      "webhookId": "wait-replicate-initial-hook"
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "method": "GET",
        "url": "=https://api.replicate.com/v1/predictions/{{ $('HTTP — Replicate Create').item.json.id }}",
        "authentication": "genericCredentialType",
        "genericAuthType": "httpHeaderAuth",
        "options": {
          "timeout": 60000,
          "response": {
            "response": {
              "neverError": true
            }
          }
        }
      },
      "id": "http-replicate-poll",
      "name": "HTTP — Replicate Poll",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.httpRequest",
      "typeVersion": 4.2,
      "position": [1200, 520],
      "onError": "continueRegularOutput",
      "credentials": {
        "httpHeaderAuth": {
          "id": "REPLICATE_CREDENTIAL_ID",
          "name": "Replicate API Token"
        }
      }
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": {
            "caseSensitive": true,
            "leftValue": "",
            "typeValidation": "strict"
          },
          "conditions": [
            {
              "id": "rep-succeeded",
              "leftValue": "={{ $json.status }}",
              "rightValue": "succeeded",
              "operator": {
                "type": "string",
                "operation": "equals"
              }
            }
          ],
          "combinator": "and"
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "if-replicate-succeeded",
      "name": "IF Replicate Succeeded?",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [1440, 520]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "conditions": {
          "options": {
            "caseSensitive": true,
            "leftValue": "",
            "typeValidation": "strict"
          },
          "conditions": [
            {
              "id": "rep-failed",
              "leftValue": "={{ $json.status }}",
              "rightValue": "failed",
              "operator": {
                "type": "string",
                "operation": "equals"
              }
            },
            {
              "id": "rep-canceled",
              "leftValue": "={{ $json.status }}",
              "rightValue": "canceled",
              "operator": {
                "type": "string",
                "operation": "equals"
              }
            }
          ],
          "combinator": "or"
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "if-replicate-failed",
      "name": "IF Replicate Failed?",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.if",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [1680, 680]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "amount": 30,
        "unit": "seconds"
